<template>
  <body>
  <el-form
      ref="ruleForm"
      :model="ruleForm"
      :rules="editRules"
      label-width="120px"
      class="demo-ruleForm"
      :size="formSize"
  >
    <el-form-item label="请输入新密码" prop="pw1" ref="pw1">
      <el-input v-model="ruleForm.pw1"></el-input>
    </el-form-item>
    <el-form-item label="请再次确认密码" prop="pw2" ref="pw2">
      <el-input v-model="ruleForm.pw2"></el-input>
    </el-form-item>

    <el-form-item>
      <el-button type="primary" @click="submitForm" >确认修改</el-button>
    </el-form-item>
  </el-form>
  </body>
</template>
<!--<script src="../assets/js/resetpasswords.js" type="text/javascript">-->
<!--</script>-->


<style scoped>
@import "../assets/css/resetPassword.css";
</style>
